Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:02.17,OP-jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}心に呼びかける君のせいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:01.68,OP,,0,0,0,,I guess that's your fault for calling out to my heart
